  "narrative": "skf-forger is a well-architected hub agent with clean delegation, lean token footprint (82 lines / ~1570 tokens), and strong defensive patterns. Its primary strength is doing exactly one thing well: presenting a persona, routing to sub-skills, and staying out of their way. The primary opportunity is that the activation experience treats all users identically — the same 14-item ceremony for first-timers and experts alike — while the lifecycle knowledge that could guide users sits behind an obscure inline action.",
